race.description: C T Electric / Elders Guyra Benchmark 58 Handicap
race.comment: DIPIERDOMENICO (6) in peak condition for this and has a solid record on his home track. Kept finding from the wide gate when a game fourth over 2370m at Grafton. Maps to stalk the speed and no excuses today. A TENT HUT (2) back in grade and has a victory over the 1800m. Just over three weeks between runs when a battling sixth over 1600m at Coonabarabran in C3 class. Key jockey change and has solid prospects. CHEEKY SECRETS (9) on the quick back up again after stretching out in trip for a plugging fourth over 2200m at Dubbo on November 1. Has her share of talent and this trip suits. TYCOON LAD (8) best performance in four starts when kept fresh for a game second over 1600m at Tamworth. Trained locally and stays in the calculations. TOULON FACTOR (4) raced himself into form with a surprise on-pace win over 1900m at this track. Can surprise a few of these again with the 3kg claim.
